    <item>
      <title>Dec 25 Art mix by Dmitry Brushray</title>
      <link>https://artbrushray.github.io/posts/dec25mix/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2026 23:53:00 +0300</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://artbrushray.github.io/posts/dec25mix/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Mix of my artworks around December 2025&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Metal always endures&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://artbrushray.github.io/img/2025/crippled-knight-by-brushray.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Stationary canon from Imperial Knight, fan art by Dmitry Brushray&#34;  /&gt;

I saw a kitbash or maybe it was somethin official where the head place of a knight was taken by huge two barrels gun. I love more palsma so it just came to me to make some sort of a stationary weapon from knight leftovers which main purpose is to carry titan class plasma as a stationary canon. So I decided to experiment with this, thought people would like something unusuall.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
